<section class="faq-section">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="faq-container">

        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
                How often should RO filters be changed?
                <span>+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>RO filters should be replaced every 6 to 12 months depending on water quality and usage.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
                Do you provide AMC services?
                <span>+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes, we offer affordable Annual Maintenance Contracts covering regular service and filter replacement.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
                Which RO brands do you service?
                <span>+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>We service all major RO brands including Kent, Aquaguard, Livpure, Pureit, and more.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
                How much does RO service cost?
                <span>+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Basic RO servicing starts from ₹499. The cost may vary depending on spare parts required.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

